Title: Tag groups: Help texts can be configured
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1573056414
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

In the {{Edit tag group}} dialog an optional help text can be configured. The
help texts appear on the {{Tag groups}} and {{Properties of host}} page if the
context help texts is toggled top right.
